
Pimply is a GTK+2 wallpaper changer.

Dependencies: gtk+2, glib
Versions: tested with gtk+ 2.12, glib 2.16

Written by: Lil AZ aka wisd0me <ak47izatool !dogg gmail d0t com>
Bug reports/other feedback is appreciated.

Compile:
 $ make

Install (to /usr/local by default):
 # make install
or
 # make PREFIX=/usr install

Usage:
To set background just run pimply.
To see command line options (like restore previously set background), run:
$ pimply --help

enjoy ;>
